Package: LD
Type: Package
Date: 2018-01-06
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Title: Linkage Disequilibrium Analysis
Description: This package provides functions that automatize a
    workflow of computations for linkage disequilibrium analysis.
    It quickly computes provided functions in 'rehh' (citation)
    package which has a set of algorithms previously described 
    in the scientific literature.    
Author: Cainã Max Couto-Silva
Maintainer: Cainã Max Couto-Silva <cmcouto.silva@usp.br>
URL: https://github.com/cmcouto-silva/LD
BugReports: https://github.com/cmcouto-silva/LD/issues
License: GPL-2 | GPL-3
Imports:
    rehh,
    gtools,
    data.table,
    WriteXLS
Depends: R (>= 3.4)
